thread.title: Multiple people injured in Florida high school shooting

title: Multiple people injured in Florida high school shooting
text:
Multiple people injured in Florida high school shooting 3:52pm EST - 00:28 
At least 20 people were injured when a gunman opened fire at a Florida high school, local media reported, with dozens of police and emergency officials surrounding the building while students fled with their arms in the air.
